Package se.arkalix.core.plugin

Arrowhead Kalix Core Service Plugins

This package contains various plugins useful for interacting with the Arrowhead Framework core services.

Currently, the most significant component of this package is the HttpJsonCloudPlugin class.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ArEventPublish
    Represents an Arrowhead event publishing service.
    ArEventSubscribe
    Represents an Arrowhead event subscription service.
    ArEventSubscriptionHandler
    An event receiver associated with a particular topic, a set of possible publishing systems and a required set of metadata parameters.
    ArEventUnsubscribe
    Represents an Arrowhead event subscription cancellation service.
    ArOrchestration
    Represents an Arrowhead orchestration service.
    ArServiceDiscovery
    Represents an Arrowhead service discovery service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HttpJsonCloudPlugin
    HTTP/JSON cloud plugin.
    HttpJsonCloudPlugin.Builder
    Builder useful for constructing HttpJsonCloudPlugin instances.
    HttpJsonCoreIntegrator Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
    HttpJsonCoreIntegrator.Builder Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
    HttpJsonEventPublish
    A remote ArEventPublish service that is communicated with via HTTP/JSON in either secure or insecure mode.
    HttpJsonEventSubscribe
    A remote ArEventSubscribe service that is communicated with via HTTP/JSON in either secure or insecure mode.
    HttpJsonEventSubscriptionPlugin
    HTTP/JSON event subscription plugin.
    HttpJsonEventSubscriptionPlugin.Builder
    Builder used to construct HttpJsonEventSubscriptionPlugin instances.
    HttpJsonEventUnsubscribe
    A remote ArEventUnsubscribe service that is communicated with via HTTP/JSON in either secure or insecure mode.
    HttpJsonOrchestration
    A remote ArOrchestration service that is communicated with via HTTP/JSON in either secure or insecure mode.
    HttpJsonServiceDiscovery
    A remote ArServiceDiscovery service that is communicated with via HTTP/JSON in either secure or insecure mode.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ArOrchestrationStrategy
    Enumerates the different kind of strategies that can be used when querying an orchestration service for services to consume.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ArCoreIntegrationException
    Signifies the failure to complete a core integration task.
